{"type":null,"faqId":44884,"title":"如何设置唤醒词","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">在EMUI 3.1系统，点击“设置”，在“全部设置”页签点击“智能辅助”区域的“更多 </span><span class=\"s2\">&gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">语音唤醒“，然后点击”唤醒词 </span><span class=\"s2\">&gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">自定义唤醒词“，根据屏幕提示操作，即可自定义设置新的唤醒词。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161824\" style=\"width:2.6034722in;height:4.5902777in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161825\" style=\"width:2.5909722in;height:4.5909724in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161826\" style=\"width:2.625in;height:4.5201387in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161827\" style=\"width:2.5527778in;height:4.5194445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"385","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409277000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":7,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0